    "en": {
      "title": "A coconut fell on the head of a person who was in the gas queue and went to the hospital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Pitigala police said that a coconut fell on the head of a person standing in the gas queue in the Pitigala area today (21st) and he was taken to the hospital with serious injuries.",
        "The police say that a father of three residing in Pitigala Idipalagoda area has been hospitalized.",
        "This coconut has fallen on the head of a person who was standing in the gas queue at Pitigala Idipalegoda school grounds for five days now.",
        "Elpitiya hospital sources say that the condition of the person whose head the coconut fell on is serious. Pitigala Police is conducting further investigations in this regard."
      ],
